{
	"info": {
		"name": "JobConnect RAG System",
		"description": "Full API collection for JobConnect recruitment system with RAG-powered AI chat. Features vector-based CV-job matching, Ollama/Qwen2.5 integration, and pgvector semantic search.\n\n## Pre-Requisites\n1. Create a Postman Environment with:\n   - `baseUrl` = `http://localhost:3000`\n   - `accessToken` (populated automatically by Login script)\n   - `refreshToken` (populated automatically by Login script)\n   - `resumeId` (populated by CV Upload script)\n   - `jobId` (populated by Search script)\n\n## Auth Flow\nLogin → accessToken auto-saved → all protected endpoints use `{{accessToken}}` via the collection-level Authorization header.\n\n## Demo Flow\n1. Register/Login\n2. Upload CV (PDF) → wait for vectorStatus = COMPLETED\n3. Chat: \"CV của tôi hợp với job nào?\"\n4. Chat: \"So sánh CV của tôi với job React Developer\"\n5. Search: Find jobs by keyword",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "JobConnect-QA"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "🏆 Authentication",
			"description": "Register, Login, Refresh Token, and Logout endpoints. Login automatically saves accessToken and refreshToken into environment variables via post-response script.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register (Candidate)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"// =============================================",
									"// Status Code Check",
									"// =============================================",
									"pm.test('Status 201 - Created', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
									"});",
									"",
									"// =============================================",
									"// Response Time Check (< 3000ms for register)",
									"// =============================================",
									"pm.test('Response time < 3000ms', function () {",
									"    pm.expect(pm.response.responseTime).to.be.below(3000);",
									"});",
									"",
									"// =============================================",
									"// Validate Response Structure",
									"// =============================================",
									"pm.test('Response has valid structure', function () {",
									"    const json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(json.status).to.eql('success');",
									"    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('id');",
									"    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('accessToken');",
									"    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('refreshToken');",
									"    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('role');",
									"});",
									"",
									"// =============================================",
									"// Auto-Save Tokens to Environment",
									"// =============================================",
									"const json = pm.response.json();",
									"if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
									"    pm.environment.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
									"    pm.environment.set('refreshToken', json.data.refreshToken);",
									"    console.log('[Register] Tokens saved to environment');",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"Nguyễn Văn A\",\n  \"email\": \"candidate@gmail.com\",\n  \"phone\": \"0901234567\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
						}
					}
				},
